query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(c o l) */ select l.l_orderkey,
sum(l.l_extendedprice * 1 - l.l_discount) AS revenue,
o.o_orderdate,
o.o_shippriority
from customer AS c
inner join orders AS o
on c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey AND c.c_mktsegment = 'MACHINERY' AND o.o_orderdate < '1995-03-03'::date
inner join lineitem AS l
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey AND l.l_shipdate > '1995-03-03'::date group by l.l_orderkey, o.o_orderdate, o.o_shippriority order by revenue desc, o.o_orderdate;
